    "description": "<p>OUNG CONSTRUCTION (S) PTE LTD</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Oung Construction (S) Pte Ltd (OCS) is a leading marine civil engineering firm and renowned foreshore specialist in Singapore. We offer a comprehensive range of services including revetment, seawall, breakwater, and rock bund construction and maintenance, as well as reclamation, dredging, and diving services.<br>\n<br>\nRecognised for our consistent delivery of high-quality work and timely project completion, we are proud to serve as the current maintenance contractor for foreshore structures under the Building and Construction Authority (BCA) of Singapore.<br>\n<br>\nOur strong commitment to safety is reflected in our OHSAS 18001:2007 accreditation and BizSafe Star certification. With over 150,000 man-hours completed without accidents, we uphold the highest standards in workplace safety and project execution. As a B1-graded contractor, OCS remains a trusted name in Singapore’s marine and coastal infrastructure landscape.</p>",
